Adjusted predictions and marginal means

Under the hood, marginaleffects’s predictions function uses the insight package to retrieve adjusted predictions from a wide variety of models. Currently, insight supports over many model types, and most should work out-of-the-box with the predictions function. If you run into problems, do not hesitate to report them on Github or via email.
